tbah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-7xq","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":4202,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/prophet-prayer-sermon-moderate\/","url_meta":{"origin":28980,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Moderation: The Prophet\u2019s prayer and sermon were moderate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: I was praying with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and his prayer was of moderate length and his sermon was of moderate length. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 866 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0623\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/mindful-friday-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28980,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jumu\u2019ah: Have presence at sermon, be near to Imam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe present at the sermon and come close to the Imam. Verily, a man continues to distance himself until he is delayed from Paradise, even though he will eventually enter it.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3213,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/16\/no-talking-jumuah-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28980,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah: Not allowed to speak during Friday Sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you tell your companion to be quiet on Friday while the Imam is speaking, you have spoken improperly.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 892, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 851 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Al-Nawawi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/attend-sermon-quietly\/","url_meta":{"origin":28980,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Minor sins forgiven until next Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution in the best manner, comes to Friday prayer, and listens while remaining quiet, his\u00a0sins will be forgiven until the next Friday and an additional three days, but whoever plays with pebbles has behaved\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15815,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/special-moment-friday-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":28980,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Special moment for Friday supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Burdah reported: Abdullah ibn Umar said to me, \u201cHave you heard anything narrated by your father from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about the special moment on Friday?\u201d I said, \u201cYes. I heard him narrate that the Messenger of Allah said, 'It is the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/salat-al-eid-then-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28980,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet prays Eid, then gives sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: I witnessed the prayer on the day of Eid al-Fitr with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, may Allah be pleased with them. They performed the prayer before the sermon, then would deliver the sermon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","wi